g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港有你哋班垃圾，客戶服務先會咁落後"},{"pid":"67b91dd1472cbc570280564e26905d7ea4135b63","tid":59711,"uid":46575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:50:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來依家買野唔比格價又唔比試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港有你哋班垃圾，客戶服務先會咁落後</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔比 但個比率唔會係試十件買一件囉<br />\n如果買既係車唔係衫，人地仲會唔會理你<br />\n有好多時真係自己做過先好咁大聲講<br />\n同埋我個人黎講試完一定買，如果明知唔岩我仲試黎做咩"},{"pid":"b7a701b7ee6df4c2d6b72fb9d863a9ea49d12af5","tid":59711,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果同樣同係西客，但係大陸狗問多過問，又唔會下下投訴你，又唔會試一大論又唔撚賣，又唔會永遠係你就黎收舖果陣搞鳩你，你就唔會咁樣問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好撚憎大陸狗，但係呢方面大陸狗真係做得比香港人好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸狗係旅行。豪爽少少係正常"},{"pid":"b09f73dde815fd0fb407e489345a76fedb0e95ab","tid":59711,"uid":13079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:05:38.000Z","msg":"香港sales 同餐廳waiter 一樣咁on9<br />\n比D on9大陸西搞到好似一定要買咁<br />\n屌你做賣野就係有客買有客唔買架啦<br />\n試下又話嫌人唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔撚知以為你貼錢送件野比我咁<br />\n食野又係坐多一陣好似要你條命咁撚樣"},{"pid":"b1bb6cb54cd97f16380c8e91725be2192577eb3e","tid":59711,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:05:41.000Z","msg":"點解大陸人要開個post搞分化香港人？"},{"pid":"3ddb78886f753196027a73b1b95cab74fa40fdbd","tid":59711,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:07:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來依家買野唔比格價又唔比試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港有你哋班垃圾，客戶服務先會咁落後</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔比 但個比率唔會係試十件買一件囉<br />\n如果買既係車唔係衫，人地仲會唔會理你<br />\n有好多時真係自己做過先好咁大聲講<br />\n同埋我個人黎講試完一定買，如果明知唔岩我仲試黎做咩</blockquote><br />\nsales出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ba6009c0b5bdfa09c16a721fd9e5bf757bf092","tid":59711,"uid":46575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原來依家買野唔比格價又唔比試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港有你哋班垃圾，客戶服務先會咁落後</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係話唔比 但個比率唔會係試十件買一件囉<br />\n如果買既係車唔係衫，人地仲會唔會理你<br />\n有好多時真係自己做過先好咁大聲講<br />\n同埋我個人黎講試完一定買，如果明知唔岩我仲試黎做咩</blockquote><br />\nsales出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前係依家唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339e5cda98836e1bd4b9b8bba76ce26ddc0f33e6","tid":59711,"uid":36619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:11:41.000Z","msg":"知左個價又要試 試完話貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cc379a2741d950a7d89749a921fbbd553c205c","tid":59711,"uid":25356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為太多香港窮撚唔買問三問四<br />\n參考資料: 本人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes<br />\n阻撚住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n格下價都要掛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n格下價係得，憎d 丐幫買公價野都要格價。"},{"pid":"a2d6a095e8f440fa210fe6a7479c51c91e7a4c1d","tid":59711,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:13:00.000Z","msg":"買得少又多要求"},{"pid":"34939c44f6099b0512e745054f9e7fb99a6582cf","tid":59711,"uid":9541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T02:21:44.000Z","msg":"就好似啲客拎住幾球周銀行格定期息口<br />\n仲要當正自己係大客仔一樣"},{"pid":"fde4ac0ac45f4d7e40e05d74a0d3609b9c13f201","tid":59711,"uid":38552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:03:11.000Z","msg":"香港本地客多西人係不爭既事實，唔係要你入到黎試，試完一定要同我買撚左佢，亦都唔係要你入得黎就要買野，唔比問長問短。<br />\n    但你咪撚on99咁試完款再試岩size,先黎考慮個價錢問題，同有無贈品送既問題，咪張女人街文化通用全個零售市場，以為你試完同個sales講價錢唔岩喊走，個sales 就會拉住你比返你心目中價你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n   應該立法強制年青人一畢業就要做半年sales ,體驗一下<br />\n利申：目前非零售業者"},{"pid":"dac13ab6b6bd1263353ea6d4604b50235f0b4815","tid":59711,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"一樣大把西客狗眼看人低 睇唔起人做sales<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}